Itu sama sekali tidak sakit.

437
00:27:21,988 --> 00:27:23,348
Hei, Nona Dam.

438
00:27:24,268 --> 00:27:25,368
Nona Dam.

439
00:27:32,148 --> 00:27:33,858
Bisakah kau memberitahuku?

